{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["Preheat oven to 170°C then grease and line a square cake tin (20 cm) with baking paper.","Place sugar, flour, cocoa powder, oil, milk, baking powder, vanilla extract and eggs in mixing bowl then mix <b>15 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then mix again <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Transfer mixture to prepared cake tin. Bake for 25-30 minutes (170°C) until a skewer inserted in centre comes out clean. Allow to cool in tin for 5 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to cool completely. Meanwhile, clean and dry mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Icing","content":["When cake is cool, place chocolate in mixing bowl and grate <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then melt <b>3 min\/50°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add sour cream and mix <b>30 sec\/speed 2<b>. Finish mixing by hand with spatula.","Immediately ice top of cooled cake. Cut in squares or transfer to an airtight container to store until needed."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["120 g sunflower oil, plus extra for greasing","120 g caster sugar","120 g self-raising flour","30 g cocoa powder","100 g whole milk","1 tsp baking powder","1 tsp real vanilla extract","2 large eggs"]},{"title":"Icing","content":["125 g dark chocolate (70% cocoa solids), small pieces or callets","125 g sour cream"]}],"id":"r120913","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-GiSQEvawg4g\/XZWrhMvqs3I\/AAAAAAAAfoc\/TF_5TC_x84sRH4rXNYULsfqblnvpjX41gCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ntkcZQj8oXgXrVr3.png","title":"Easy Chocolate Cake","publishedAt":"2016-07-11T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.4 g","fat":"24.5 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"30.5 g","calories":"1523 kJ \/ 364 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking paper, square cake tin (20 cm), palito ou espeto, wire rack, forno,","hintsAndTricks":["Any icing can be used such as chocolate buttercream or whipped cream with fresh berries.","The chocolate cake can also be baked in a round cake tin (Ø 20 cm) if preferred."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 15m","9 pieces"]}